{"tid":1434544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 星期六收到風！","createTime":"2019-08-08T21:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T23:36:20.000Z","uid":200974,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1b10d12f7ca1bd7b02deff0b0743fb6ce834f606","tid":1434544,"uid":200974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:00:38.000Z","msg":"雖然我小出po 但千真萬確！<br />\n<br />\n話說今日同朋友去食飯<br />\n咁出面就有幾個大陸佬都入黎食飯<br />\n開頭都冇為意 後來佢用d唔知咩話溝通<br />\n而咁岩我朋友就鄉下福建 一聽就知係福建話<br />\n<br />\n咁我同佢就一直都冇出聲 而我朋友應該一直聽緊<br />\n到佢地走左 我朋友就話原來佢地講緊<br />\n星期六打算係荃灣北角搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以星期六各位手足記得小心d<br />\n<br />\nBe water!"},{"pid":"962ace190211385f26de0733581b59978fa38d9e","tid":1434544,"uid":243854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:03:09.000Z","msg":"相又影唔到，音又錄唔到<br />\n你講有幾個外星人喺度討論侵略地球都得啦<br />\nBTW有咪要班福建仔變晒豬頭返去"},{"pid":"1718c0dfc10053e6fb8c29eade9ed86ce1a32148","tid":1434544,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:04:05.000Z","msg":"咦，班流浮山刀手入丁天油圍未呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7833aa0fad3bc64aba007c8293705e80441d821d","tid":1434544,"uid":132625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:04:44.000Z","msg":"負評<br />\n不推文回覆<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"75d42b576274c30c9a223920677a76df03482bb7","tid":1434544,"uid":139507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:07:44.000Z","msg":"負評<br />\n不推文回覆<br />\n上一頁"},{"pid":"413f54d093da8568c809653bd9313bec3a6fe409","tid":1434544,"uid":139190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T21:15:05.000Z","msg":"係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又會<span style=\"color: red;\">咁啱</span>比你撞到嗰班人 佢地又<span style=\"color: red;\">咁啱</span>用福建話 你又<span style=\"color: red;\">咁啱</span>有個fd識聽<br />\n<br />\n負評 0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 